data.description: Welcome home to your picturesque, full brick, 3-bed, 2-bathroom rancher! You'll love the convenience of the wrap-around driveway, the comfort of the covered porch, and the freedom of the bonus garage space!  Inside, you'll find the open living room with smooth ceilings and hardwood floors throughout, the updated granite countertops and pantry in the kitchen, and a separate dining room with an accent wall! The house also features a private en-suite off the master bedroom and a large, separate laundry room.  Outside, you'll love the awesome yard with an oversized concrete pad for outdoor entertaining and an additional detached garage for storage, a workshop, a home gym, or a craft room!
